universe u

constant obj : Type u

constant Cat : obj
constant Dog : obj
constant Rabbit : obj
constant Squirrel : obj

constant Eats : obj → obj → Prop
constant Sees : obj → obj → Prop
constant Likes : obj → obj → Prop
constant Round : obj → Prop
constant Big : obj → Prop
constant Red : obj → Prop
constant Green : obj → Prop

axiom T1 : Eats Cat Dog
axiom T2 : Eats Cat Rabbit
axiom T3 : Eats Cat Squirrel
axiom T4 : Red Cat
axiom T5 : Sees Cat Dog
axiom T6 : Sees Cat Rabbit
axiom T7 : ¬ Sees Cat Squirrel
axiom T8 : Eats Dog Cat
axiom T9 : Eats Dog Squirrel
axiom T10 : Likes Dog Rabbit
axiom T11 : Likes Dog Squirrel
axiom T12 : Likes Rabbit Dog
axiom T13 : Likes Rabbit Squirrel
axiom T14 : Sees Rabbit Squirrel
axiom T15 : Round Squirrel
axiom T16 : Sees Squirrel Rabbit

axiom R1 : ∀ x : obj, Big x → Likes x Cat
axiom R2 : ∀ x : obj, Round x → Big x
axiom R3 : ∀ x : obj, Eats x Squirrel ∧ Eats Squirrel Dog → Eats x Dog
axiom R4 : ∀ x : obj, Eats x Cat → Round x
axiom R5 : Green Cat ∧ Eats Cat Rabbit → Big Cat
axiom R6 : ∀ x : obj, Likes x Rabbit ∧ Sees Rabbit Cat → Likes Rabbit Dog
axiom R7 : ∀ x : obj, Eats x Squirrel ∧ Eats x Dog → Red Dog
axiom R8 : ∀ x : obj, Big x ∧ Sees x Rabbit → Eats Rabbit Cat
axiom R9 : Eats Cat Squirrel → ¬ Eats Squirrel Cat

theorem rabbit_likes_cat : Likes Rabbit Cat :=
begin
  apply R1,
  apply R2,
  apply R4,
  exact T8,
end
